# Phase / Epic / Task Authoring

**Before creating phases/tasks:** read `docs/09-development/PHASE_EPIC_TASK_AUTHORING_RULES.md`

## Structure (mandatory)

```
Phases/Phase-N-Name/Epic-NN-Name/TASK-NNN-kebab-slug.md
```

- **One task = one `.md` file**
- **Epic README required** — task index + depends
- **Phase README required** — execution order

## Every task must have

Metadata (Priority, Depends, Blocks) · Acceptance criteria · Full tech spec · Files · Steps · Edge cases · Tests · Policy alignment · References

## Prisma tasks

Include ALL base fields + EXCELLENCE §8 entity fields + soft delete. `onDelete: Restrict` — never Cascade hard delete.

## Flow/auth tasks

Document all actors + order (no register/verify contradiction). Mermaid/ascii flow.

## Missing task types (check each phase)

Soft delete/restore · Onboarding flow · CI hard-delete grep · Seed role clone · Module skeleton · Vertical slice E2E

## Template

Copy from `docs/09-development/TASK-TEMPLATE.md`

## Review gate

Task self-score ≥ **95/100** — PHASE_EPIC_TASK_AUTHORING_RULES §10

